7 [ animals - commercial pet breeders - license number
8 – advertisements - Oklahoma Department of
9 Agriculture, Food, and Forestry - rules and fines –
10 codification - effective date ]
11
12
13 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
14 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
15 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 30.17 of Title 4, unless there
16 is created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
17 A. All commercial pet breeders under this title shall list
18 their commercial pet breeder's license number, as issued by the
19 Oklahoma Department of Agriculture, Food, and Forestry, on all
20 advertisements for pet sales.
21 B. The Oklahoma Department of Agriculture, Food, and Forestry
22 shall promulgate rules to implement and enforce the provisions of
23 this section, including, but not limited to, setting fines for
24 noncompliance with this section.
ENGR. H. B. NO. 3391 Page 1

1 SECTION 2. This act shall become effective November 1, 2026.
2 Passed the House of Representatives the 24th day of March, 2026.
